            p Below is a map I created of the world. Not everything is included, but everything related to the story so far should be there.
                br
                span(class='note d-none d-md-block') Note: My map is currently only avaible on desktop devices.
        p= mobile
        if mobile
            section(class='')
                div(class='mobile-map-show')
